Amir Khan will fight Chris Algieri at welterweight on May 30 . 
  The Bolton fighter had been under pressure to fight Kell Brook in June . 
  Khan has announced he will fight former light-welterweight world champion Al gieri in New York next month . 
  The 28-year-old has been linked with bouts against Adrien Broner and Keith Thurman . 
  Khan said his next fight will be against Algieri in May . 
  The fight will take place at the Barclays Center in New York . 
  Khan lost his last fight against Manny Pacquiao in November last year . 
 